                  Cha.
                  Harke, harke.
               
               
                  Andr.
                  The Coach that brings the faire
Lady.
               
               
                  Enter LEVVIS, ANGELLINA,
Ladies, NOTARY, &amp;c.
               
               
                  And.
                  Now you may see her.
               
               
                  Cha.
                  Sure this should be modest;
                  But I doe not truly know what women make of it,
                  
                     Andrew; she has a face lookes like a story,
