                  Bri.
                  Ile answer you, here's good meate.
               
               
                  Mira.
                  But your sawce is
scurvie,
                  It is not season'd with the sharpnesse of discretion.
               
               
                  Eust.
                  It seemes your anger is at me, deare Uncle.
               
               
                  
                  Mir.
