                  Eust.
                  I would doe much Sir,
                  But still my reputation!
               
               
                  Mir.
                  
                     Charles shall give you
                  All decent satisfaction; nay, joyne hands,
                  And heartily; why this is done like brothers;
                  And old as I am, in this cause that concernes
